text_blocks.text: There should be laws which limit the amount of salt added to manufactured foods
When eating out at restaurants/cafes/pubs, I find that lower salt options are not readily available
Himalayan salt, pink salt, sea salt and gourmet salts are healthier than regular table salt
It is hard to understand sodium informationdisplayed on food labels
My health would improve if I reduced the amount of salt in my diet
I believe salt needs to be added to food to make it tasty
